OL,3,CBadenoch under pressure to back up
OL,4,Cclaims ex-Post Office boss lied
OL,6,FIn an interview with The Sunday Times,
OL,7,FMr Staunton said a senior civil
OL,8,Fservant asked him to delay offering
OL,9,Fcompensation to sub-postmasters and to
OL,10,F"limp into the election".
OL,12,FMr Staunton, who took up the role in
OL,13,F2022 was sacked by the business
OL,14,Fsecretary last month.
OL,16,FHe told The Sunday Times Ms Badenoch
OL,17,Fhad said "someone's got to take the
OL,18,Frap" for the Horizon scandal, and that
OL,19,Fhe only found out about being sacked
OL,20,Fafter a phone call from Sky News.
