OL,6,FIn a lengthy post on X, the business
OL,7,Fsecretary said his interview was "full
OL,8,Fof lies about our conversation during
OL,9,Fhis dismissal".
OL,11,FMs Badenoch said the comments were a
OL,12,F"disgraceful misrepresentation of my
OL,13,Fconversation with him and the reasons
OL,14,Ffor his dismissal.J"Henry Staunton had
OL,15,Fa lack of grip getting justice for
OL,16,Fpostmasters. The serious concerns over
OL,17,Fhis conduct were the reasons I asked
OL,18,Fhim to step down.J"That he chose to
OL,19,Frun to the media with made up
OL,20,Fanecdotes and a series of falsehoods,
OL,21,Fconfirms I made the correct decision."
