OL,6,FKemi Badenoch, who ran for the Tory
OL,7,Fleadership after the fall of Boris
OL,8,FJohnson, is said to be the next Tory
OL,9,Fleader in the eyes of many plotters
OL,10,Fagainst Rishi Sunak.
OL,12,FWhile she has distanced herself from
OL,13,FTory plotters in the media, Ms
OL,14,FBadenoch regularly tops the rankings
OL,15,Ffor most popular Cabinet member.
OL,17,FAlso serving as the women and
OL,18,Fequalities minister, the MP for
OL,19,FSaffron Walden has become known for
OL,20,Fher strong views on gender identity.
