OL,6,FWhat is the Post Office Horizon
OL,7,Fscandal?
OL,9,FThe long-running battle for justice
OL,10,Faccelerated dramatically after the
OL,11,Fpublic outcry provoked by the.
OL,13,FMore than 10.3 million people have
OL,14,Fwatched the final episode of the
OL,15,Fseries making it one of the .
OL,17,FIn 1999 the Post Office introduced
OL,18,Fdigital accounting software named
OL,19,FHorizon - created by Japanese tech
OL,20,Ffirm Fujitsu - which replaced the
OL,21,Fpaper-based process of the past.
