OL,3,CBadenoch under pressure to back up
OL,4,Cclaims ex-Post Office boss lied
OL,6,FBut it soon became clear to some sub-
OL,7,Fpostmasters that the software was
OL,8,Fcreating discrepancies in their
OL,9,Faccounts, making it look like cash was
OL,10,Fmissing.
OL,12,FA sub-postmaster is someone not
OL,13,Fdirectly employed by the Post Office,
OL,14,Fwho runs a separate retail business
OL,15,Fwhich hosts a Post Office facility on
OL,16,Ftheir site.
OL,18,FThe idea is that an in-house Post
OL,19,FOffice would drive customers to their
OL,20,Fbusiness.
