OL,3,CBadenoch under pressure to back up
OL,4,Cclaims ex-Post Office boss lied
OL,6,FBut many didn't - and the Post Office,
OL,7,Fwhich has the power to run private
OL,8,Fprosecutions, sought to have many sub-
OL,9,Fpostmasters convicted of fraud and
OL,10,Ftheft.
OL,12,FWatch the trailer for ITV's Mr Bates
OL,13,Fvs The Post Office
OL,15,FBetween 1999 and 2015, 736 sub-
OL,16,Fpostmasters were wrongfully convicted
OL,17,Fbut concerns with the faulty Horizon
OL,18,Fsystem were raised in court as early
OL,19,Fas 2003.
