OL,3,CBadenoch under pressure to back up
OL,4,Cclaims ex-Post Office boss lied
OL,6,FBy 2012, potential problems with
OL,7,FHorizon were so apparent the Post
OL,8,FOffice launched a review to satisfy
OL,9,Fpoliticians who had been complaining
OL,10,Fon behalf of their aggrieved
OL,11,Fconstituents.
OL,13,FThe Post Office however continued
OL,14,Fprosecuting sub-postmasters until 2015
OL,15,Fbut the miscarriage of justice was
OL,16,Fonly confirmed in 2019 when the High
OL,17,FCourt ruled that Horizon was to blame.
