OL,6,FA number of compensation schemes were
OL,7,Fintroduced by the government and #87
OL,8,Fmillion was eventually paid out
OL,9,Fthrough the Horizon Shortfall Scheme
OL,10,Fto more than 2,500 sub-postmasters who
OL,11,Flost money but weren't convicted.
OL,13,FTo date, just 93 convictions have been
OL,14,Foverturned but the government recently
OL,15,Fannounced legislation which will give
OL,16,Fblanket exonerations to all those
OL,17,Fwrongfully convicted.
